data.description: $3,000 LENDER CREDIT WITH PREFERRED LENDER! Explore this 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home with a spacious 3-car garage, situated within the highly regarded Moore School District. NEW: interior paint, AC, dishwasher, and smart range! Inside you’ll find generously sized bedrooms, including a primary suite with an oversized walk-in closet with third row, seasonal hanging, and an en-suite bathroom featuring both a stand-alone shower and a garden tub. The heart of the home boasts an open kitchen layout with a well-crafted kitchen island, ample cabinetry, a convenient pantry, and an eat-in dining space. Additionally, there’s a second, formal dining room for added flexibility. Warm up by the cozy gas fireplace in the living area. Step outside to enjoy privacy with a charming privacy fence and the convenience of an in-ground sprinkler system. The built-out attic space is ready to be customized and completed to add space and immediate value. Safety features include an in-ground storm shelter and fire-suppression sprinklers. This residence seamlessly combines practicality with comfort, making it an ideal place to call home.
